===========================
NEWS for 0.3.1 (2014-09-29)
===========================

Changes since 0.3.0 (2014-09-19)
================================

[bubbles]

* fix bubbles randomness

Changes since 0.2.0 (2014-08-09)
================================

[clock]

* second hand can be set to OFF (default), BLOB (default on), or LINE, e.g.
  -s0, -sBLOB, or --second=LINE.
